{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"6ob2g","text":"What is adversarial machine learning?","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cgai","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bhpoc","text":"Hello, world, and welcome back to the blog! In today's post I'll give a brief introduction to adversarial machine learning. What is it and why should we care? Let's dive into it!","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3os4r","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aka1e","text":"A looming tension","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d3oj","text":"Machine learning is booming. Engineers and researchers can field new applications in a fraction of the time. Machine learning models recommend the shows we watch, filter the media we consume, and diagnose our diseases. We use them for the facial recognition we use to unlock our cell phones. Virtually every industry is being both disrupted and revolutionized by machine learning.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a5oq7","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1t3l8","text":"But behind this explosive growth lies an emerging threat. Machine learning models are vulnerable to a kind of attack that ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}